data.description: Wow!  Rare opportunity top floor condo at Peachtree Place with extra high ceilings, covered parking and just steps to all the amenities!  This immaculate unit features hardwood floors, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, 2 closets, Juliet balcony, crown moulding, covered parking and more!  Peachtree Place boasts great amenities including a 24 hour gated entry with attendant, resort-style pool, 2 level fitness center, business center, club room, theater room with billiards table, dog park and Luxer One package pick-up!  Walk to shops and restaurants of Brookhaven while being approx. 1 mile from Phipps and Lenox malls.  Low HOA fees of $364/mo include water, sewer and bi-weekly trash valet!  Don't miss this one!  Leasing permits ARE available now!  No Air BNB.
